# Plano de Redesign de Cores

## Paleta de Cores

| Função | Cor | Hex |
|--------|-----|-----|
| Principal (backgrounds) | Azul Petróleo | #013648 |
| Secundária (textos) | Dourado | #EAD8AC |
| Bordas e detalhes | Preto | #000000 |

## Arquivos a Modificar

### 1. Configuração Principal

#### tailwind.config.ts

Substituir todas as definições de cores:

```typescript
colors: {
  border: '#000000',
  input: '#000000',
  ring: '#EAD8AC',
  background: '#013648',
  foreground: '#EAD8AC',
  primary: {
    DEFAULT: '#013648',
    foreground: '#EAD8AC',
  },
  secondary: {
    DEFAULT: '#013648',
    foreground: '#EAD8AC',
  },
  destructive: {
    DEFAULT: '#013648',
    foreground: '#EAD8AC',
  },
  muted: {
    DEFAULT: '#013648',
    foreground: '#EAD8AC',
  },
  accent: {
    DEFAULT: '#EAD8AC',
    foreground: '#013648',
  },
  popover: {
    DEFAULT: '#013648',
    foreground: '#EAD8AC',
  },
  card: {
    DEFAULT: '#013648',
    foreground: '#EAD8AC',
  },
}
```

Remover cores semânticas (success, warning, info, destructive colorido) e usar apenas a paleta definida.

#### src/app/globals.css

Atualizar variáveis CSS:

```css
:root {
  --background: 197 100% 14%;
  --foreground: 43 56% 80%;
  --card: 197 100% 14%;
  --card-foreground: 43 56% 80%;
  --popover: 197 100% 14%;
  --popover-foreground: 43 56% 80%;
  --primary: 197 100% 14%;
  --primary-foreground: 43 56% 80%;
  --secondary: 197 100% 14%;
  --secondary-foreground: 43 56% 80%;
  --muted: 197 100% 14%;
  --muted-foreground: 43 56% 80%;
  --accent: 43 56% 80%;
  --accent-foreground: 197 100% 14%;
  --destructive: 197 100% 14%;
  --destructive-foreground: 43 56% 80%;
  --border: 0 0% 0%;
  --input: 0 0% 0%;
  --ring: 43 56% 80%;
}
```

Atualizar classe `.text-gradient-gold`:

```css
.text-gradient-gold {
  color: #EAD8AC;
}
```

Atualizar classe `.card-hover`:

```css
.card-hover {
  border: 1px solid #000000;
  background-color: #013648;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
.card-hover:hover {
  border-color: #EAD8AC;
}
```

Remover classes de badges coloridos e adaptar para usar apenas dourado/preto.

### 2. Componentes de Layout

#### src/components/layout/header.tsx

- Substituir `bg-background/95` por `bg-[#013648]`
- Substituir `border-primary/20` por `border-black`
- Substituir `text-primary` por `text-[#EAD8AC]`
- Substituir `text-muted-foreground` por `text-[#EAD8AC]`
- Substituir `hover:bg-secondary` por `hover:bg-[#013648]` com borda dourada

#### src/components/layout/admin-nav.tsx

- Substituir todas as referências de cores por `#013648` (fundo) e `#EAD8AC` (texto)
- Substituir `bg-primary/10` por fundo com opacidade do azul
- Substituir `text-destructive` por `text-[#EAD8AC]`
- Bordas em preto

#### src/components/layout/footer.tsx

- Substituir `bg-background` por `bg-[#013648]`
- Substituir `border-border` por `border-black`
- Manter `text-gradient-gold` (já atualizado no globals.css)
- Substituir `hover:text-primary` por `hover:text-[#EAD8AC]`

### 3. Componentes UI

#### src/components/ui/button.tsx

Atualizar variantes:

```typescript
const buttonVariants = cva(
  "... border-black ...",
  {
    variants: {
      variant: {
        default: "bg-[#EAD8AC] text-[#013648] border border-black hover:brightness-110",
        destructive: "bg-[#013648] text-[#EAD8AC] border border-black hover:opacity-90",
        outline: "border border-black bg-transparent text-[#EAD8AC] hover:bg-[#EAD8AC] hover:text-[#013648]",
        secondary: "bg-[#013648] text-[#EAD8AC] border border-black hover:opacity-90",
        ghost: "text-[#EAD8AC] hover:bg-[#EAD8AC]/10",
        link: "text-[#EAD8AC] underline-offset-4 hover:underline",
      },
    },
  }
)
```

#### src/components/ui/badge.tsx

Atualizar variantes:

```typescript
const badgeVariants = cva(
  "... border-black ...",
  {
    variants: {
      variant: {
        default: "bg-[#EAD8AC] text-[#013648] border border-black",
        secondary: "bg-[#013648] text-[#EAD8AC] border border-black",
        destructive: "bg-[#013648] text-[#EAD8AC] border border-black",
        outline: "text-[#EAD8AC] border border-black",
      },
    },
  }
)
```

Remover variantes success, warning, info.

#### src/components/ui/card.tsx

